# MindLooker Website (bemorefree.com)

A high-performance, SEO-optimized website for MindLooker - offering the MindLooker 1-on-1 session as a radically different approach to personal transformation where clients find their own answers in a completely neutral, judgment-free space.

## 🚀 Project Overview

This website serves as the primary digital presence for MindLooker, focusing on:
- Converting visitors frustrated with traditional therapy into booked sessions
- Explaining the MindLooker 1-on-1 session - our non-directive, non-evaluative approach
- Providing valuable content through blog integration
- Enabling easy booking for free trials and paid sessions

